<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idd1520035-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2023—Par. (4)(A). <ref href="/us/pl/118/31">Pub. L. 118–31</ref> substituted “an agency” for “a agency”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2002—Par. (5). <ref href="/us/pl/107/306">Pub. L. 107–306</ref> added par. (5).</p>
